headline: Edwards Lifesciences Pops On Its Bullish 2026 View Despite Mixed Fourth Quarter
summary: Edwards Lifesciences stock rose late Tuesday after earnings missed forecasts but fourth-quarter sales beat.

headline: Edwards Lifesciences Reports Fourth Quarter Results
summary: IRVINE, Calif., February 10, 2026--Edwards Lifesciences (NYSE: EW) today reported financial results for the quarter and full-year ended Dec. 31, 2025.
